\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsAjL4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsAjL4W.jpg&h=f128e56d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c6f131d81e58972a0db24d0b80e518bc934274c","tid":1524094,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cb2d024df7b98ac0bf4ae01442eb039a042cbf0","tid":1524094,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"443946a93832ef4491a054433db452feb63eab98","tid":1524094,"uid":64275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"668add7aaae013d6623eadfd16c55cf18435810d","tid":1524094,"uid":273648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"984e829816dce6d2f9c382bb328a38c3caf30fa5","tid":1524094,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:48:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ae5778cb415756e102df83094c86376aa294323","tid":1524094,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:01:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9d0332160abe8bcb64f52d8c729f4ad7912b99","tid":1524094,"uid":77490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75deabebac309c8f56bb01b96b91b1f07668ef43","tid":1524094,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbVPoOx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbVPoOx.jpg&h=c59a97e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有三罷先可以不流血不被捕又影響到政府！<br />\n<br />\n係咪為左幾百蚊就放棄你未來既自由同人生安全？<br />\n<br />\n依家黑警既濫權已經控制唔到，入地鐵無目標打完就走。<br />\n<br />\n你係咪仲可以安心番工？同我入晒機場<br />\n<br />\n推上去，9月2同9月3罷工罷市罷課！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊表態等多啲手足安心罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWgi1AT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWgi1AT.jpg&h=3fe32c1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:11:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日901 1點鐘 機場見 !!!</span> </strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入機場! 入機場! 入機場!</span><br />\n揸L爆佢春袋!!<br />\n<br />\n高舉海外文宣!! 要大大力推上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等英美就&lt;&lt;中英聯合聲明&gt;&gt;同&lt;&lt;人權及民主法案&gt;&gt;有牌揸手<br />\n要多人舉先有用!!畫面先夠力!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來想print一大堆自己帶出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但考慮到分發同大量印刷嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該見到呢堆圖嘅巴絲!我哋自己每人<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">print 10張先出門口</span></strong></span>帶入機場! <br />\n派埋比隔離左右手足朋友一齊高舉!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2hJ6TR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2hJ6TR.png&h=1cbd7c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JiqjFdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJiqjFdR.png&h=ba7711c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQL36TR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQL36TR.png&h=e3eb9cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2v0pFw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2v0pFw.png&h=3a038aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCBfdyR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCBfdyR.png&h=cb00c423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncredit to 眾多文宣巴絲<br />\n我地唔好浪費文宣巴絲們製圖嘅心血至得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好忘記今日黑警做過嘅不人道無差別毆打市民!!"},{"pid":"02431cd110c1539a990e56e16e84bae1fffa3b80","tid":1524094,"uid":178459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:20:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53828c0af405169a013619e23bfaf08c496b4710","tid":1524094,"uid":265298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:26:48.000Z","msg":"入機場前你又睇左T1攻略未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 又話壓力測試？你知唔知機場家下咩情況先？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525309</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"339381284ec89b5a3380408ed16b9110c4470ec8","tid":1524094,"uid":266878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:48:37.000Z","msg":"我咁諗，機場係一條路，不過有無諗過，呢兩個月係街，係機場，面對狗升級到開埋真鎗嘅暴力，反而，到而家，名義上發號司令嗰個林鄭，即係將香港人推出街推上絕路嗰個，佢林鄭而家日日食花生睇住你地係條街同機場由快閃，快打，咁一直無限loop,但係林鄭自己就好梳肝咁食花生。<br />\n<br />\n佢其實無乜直接受壓<br />\n<br />\n係唔係要諗下轉轉做法，直接向佢示威請願，佢先會直接受壓喎<br />\n<br />\n不過要和平咁做喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c1cd9fc09e12c73b2016e121e68288a1466f75","tid":1524094,"uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T23:18:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請聽小弟一言！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n［絕望死諫］緊急法就係靠今日機場衝突嚟做藉口出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525328</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d91cd478f5d60192de3611e71278e603bd23952","tid":1524094,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"入機場"},{"pid":"2e43dd